## Guidance

> Update ADSelfService Plus to the latest build, 6114, using the [service pack](https://www.manageengine.com/products/self-service-password/service-pack.html).

---

> CISA strongly urges organizations ensure ADSelfService Plus is not directly accessible from the internet.

